<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr" data-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMC | Engineering Marble Contractors - Premium Egyptian Stone</title>
    <meta name="description" content="EMC - Leading Egyptian marble and granite supplier since 2015. Premium natural stone for luxury projects worldwide.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Amiri:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Light Theme */
            --light-primary: #faf8f5;
            --light-secondary: #f0ebe3;
            --light-text: #1a1a2e;
            --light-text-muted: #5a5a6e;
            --light-card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            --light-card-border: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.1);
            --light-nav-bg: rgba(250, 248, 245, 0.95);

            /* Dark Theme */
            --dark-primary: #1a1a2e;
            --dark-secondary: #16213e;
            --dark-text: #f5f0e8;
            --dark-text-muted: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.7);
            --dark-card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --dark-card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --dark-nav-bg: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);

            /* Shared Colors */
            --accent-gold: #c9a962;
            --accent-gold-light: #d4af37;
            --accent-gold-dark: #a08040;
            --cream: #f5f0e8;
            --rose-accent: #d4a5a5;
            --deep-brown: #5c4033;
            --granite-black: #0f0f0f;
        }

        /* Theme Variables */
        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg-primary: var(--dark-primary);
            --bg-secondary: var(--dark-secondary);
            --text-primary: var(--dark-text);
            --text-muted: var(--dark-text-muted);
            --card-bg: var(--dark-card-bg);
            --card-border: var(--dark-card-border);
            --nav-bg: var(--dark-nav-bg);
            --hero-overlay: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.95);
            --footer-bg: var(--granite-black);
        }

        [data-theme="light"] {
            --bg-primary: var(--light-primary);
            --bg-secondary: var(--light-secondary);
            --text-primary: var(--light-text);
            --text-muted: var(--light-text-muted);
            --card-bg: var(--light-card-bg);
            --card-border: var(--light-card-border);
            --nav-bg: var(--light-nav-bg);
            --hero-overlay: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.85);
            --footer-bg: #1a1a2e;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
            transition: background 0.4s ease, color 0.4s ease;
        }

        /* RTL Support */
        [dir="rtl"] body {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] h1, [dir="rtl"] h2, [dir="rtl"] h3, [dir="rtl"] h4, [dir="rtl"] h5, [dir="rtl"] h6 {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .nav-links {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .hero-cta {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .about-grid {
            direction: rtl;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .contact-details li {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .logo {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .footer-content {
            direction: rtl;
        }

        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 1.5rem 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            background: transparent;
        }

        nav.scrolled {
            background: var(--nav-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
        }

        .logo-icon svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
        }

        .logo-tagline {
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .nav-center {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .nav-links a::after {
            left: auto;
            right: 0;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .nav-controls {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        /* Theme Toggle */
        .theme-toggle {
            width: 44px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .theme-toggle::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: 2px;
            left: 2px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle::before {
            transform: translateX(20px);
        }

        .theme-toggle .sun-icon,
        .theme-toggle .moon-icon {
            position: absolute;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .theme-toggle .sun-icon {
            right: 5px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .theme-toggle .moon-icon {
            left: 5px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .moon-icon {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .sun-icon {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Language Toggle */
        .lang-toggle {
            display: flex;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .lang-btn {
            padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .lang-btn.active {
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--dark-primary);
        }

        .menu-toggle {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1001;
        }

        .menu-toggle span {
            width: 25px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--text-primary);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 0 5%;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hero-overlay) 0%, rgba(22, 33, 62, 0.9) 100%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .hero-bg::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 800 600"><defs><linearGradient id="grad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:%23f5f0e8;stop-opacity:0.1"/><stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:%23c9a962;stop-opacity:0.05"/></linearGradient></defs><path d="M0,300 Q200,250 400,300 T800,300 L800,600 L0,600 Z" fill="url(%23grad)"/></svg>');
            background-size: cover;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .marble-texture {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            opacity: 0.03;
            background-image:
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    45deg,
                    transparent,
                    transparent 10px,
                    rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1) 10px,
                    rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1) 20px
                );
            animation: textureMove 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes textureMove {
            0% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0); }
            100% { transform: translateX(40px) translateY(40px); }
        }

        .floating-shapes {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .shape {
            position: absolute;
            border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2);
            animation: float 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .shape-1 {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            top: 10%;
            right: 10%;
            border-radius: 30% 70% 70% 30% / 30% 30% 70% 70%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .shape-2 {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 5%;
            border-radius: 70% 30% 30% 70% / 60% 40% 60% 40%;
            animation-delay: -5s;
        }

        .shape-3 {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            top: 50%;
            right: 25%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation-delay: -10s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-30px) rotate(10deg); }
        }

        .hero-content {
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.4em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .hero-subtitle {
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--cream);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        .hero-title span {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .hero-title span {
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.7);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.7s;
        }

        .hero-cta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.9s;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .btn {
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--dark-primary);
        }

        .btn-primary::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-gold-light);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--cream);
            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 3rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 2;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 1.2s;
        }

        .scroll-indicator span {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.5);
        }

        .scroll-line {
            width: 1px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent-gold), transparent);
            animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes scrollPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scaleY(0.8); }
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            padding: 10rem 5%;
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 5rem;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .section-label {
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-line {
            width: 80px;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-content h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .about-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            display: block;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .about-visual {
            position: relative;
            height: 500px;
        }

        .about-image {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .about-image-1 {
            width: 60%;
            height: 70%;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a962 0%, #a08040 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .about-image-1 {
            left: auto;
            right: 0;
        }

        .about-image-2 {
            width: 55%;
            height: 50%;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5c4033 0%, #3d2a22 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 3px solid var(--accent-gold);
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .about-image-2 {
            right: auto;
            left: 0;
        }

        .image-placeholder {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        }

        /* Products Section */
        .products {
            padding: 10rem 5%;
            background: var(--footer-bg);
            position: relative;
        }

        .products-wrapper {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .products .section-title,
        .products .section-label {
            color: var(--cream);
        }

        .product-categories {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .category-btn {
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: var(--cream);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .category-btn:hover,
        .category-btn.active {
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--dark-primary);
        }

        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.15);
        }

        .product-image {
            height: 200px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .product-image::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 50%, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 100%);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Product images - using real stone images from Unsplash */
        .product-image {
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
        }

        /* Marble images */
        .img-galala { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1635251595997-eb6c8e892ac0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-sunny { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-sinai { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616627451515-cbc80e5ece35?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-grey { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586075010923-2dd4570fb338?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-imprador { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618220179428-22790b461013?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-breccia { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557672172-298e090bd0f1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }

        /* Granite images */
        .img-black { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604068549290-dea0e4a305ca?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-halayb { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585128719715-a942e959847a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-rosa { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618047-f4b511986f0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-red { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560421683-6856ea585c78?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-verdi { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528459801416-a9e53bbf4e17?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-gold-sinai { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }

        /* Other stones */
        .img-sandstone { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544820223-c6df76dd0e29?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-basalt { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518655048521-f130df041f66?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }
        .img-mica { background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549317661-bd32c8ce0db2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80'); }

        .product-info {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .product-name {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--cream);
        }

        [dir="rtl"] .product-name {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
        }

        .product-type {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            padding: 10rem 5%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-secondary) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .service-card {
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .service-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .service-icon svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            stroke: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact {
            padding: 10rem 5%;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            position: relative;
        }

        .contact-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-info h3 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .contact-details {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .contact-details li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .contact-details svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            stroke: var(--accent-gold);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .contact-form {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 3rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-group input,
        .form-group textarea,
        .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        [data-theme="light"] .form-group input,
        [data-theme="light"] .form-group textarea,
        [data-theme="light"] .form-group select {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }

        .form-group input:focus,
        .form-group textarea:focus,
        .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .form-group textarea {
            min-height: 120px;
            resize: vertical;
        }

        .form-group select option {
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 4rem 5% 2rem;
            background: var(--footer-bg);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        }

        .footer-brand p {
            color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.6);
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .footer-links h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .footer-links ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .footer-links li {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.6);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.4);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        footer .logo-text,
        footer .logo-tagline {
            color: var(--cream);
        }

        /* Reveal Animations */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease;
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .about-grid,
            .contact-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 3rem;
            }

            .about-visual {
                height: 400px;
            }

            .footer-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }

            .nav-links {
                gap: 2rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-center {
                position: fixed;
                top: 0;
                right: -100%;
                width: 80%;
                height: 100vh;
                background: var(--bg-primary);
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 2rem;
                transition: right 0.4s ease;
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .nav-center.open {
                right: 0;
            }

            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            [dir="rtl"] .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .nav-controls {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .menu-toggle {
                display: flex;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .footer-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center;
            }

            [dir="rtl"] .footer-content {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .hero-cta {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            [dir="rtl"] .hero-cta {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .contact-details li {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            [dir="rtl"] .contact-details li {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M10 50L30 10L50 50" stroke="#c9a962" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
                    <path d="M17 50L30 25L43 50" stroke="#c9a962" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
                    <line x1="10" y1="50" x2="50" y2="50" stroke="#c9a962" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="10" y="58" fill="currentColor" font-size="8" font-family="serif">E</text>
                    <text x="27" y="58" fill="currentColor" font-size="8" font-family="serif">M</text>
                    <text x="46" y="58" fill="currentColor" font-size="8" font-family="serif">C</text>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="logo-text">EMC</div>
                <div class="logo-tagline" data-i18n="logo-tagline">Engineering Marble Contractors</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-center" id="navCenter">
            <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <li><a href="#home" data-i18n="nav-home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about" data-i18n="nav-about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#products" data-i18n="nav-products">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services" data-i18n="nav-services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact" data-i18n="nav-contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="nav-controls">
                <div class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" title="Toggle theme">
                    <svg class="moon-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <svg class="sun-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"></circle>
                        <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
                        <line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
                        <line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"></line>
                        <line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"></line>
                        <line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"></line>
                        <line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"></line>
                        <line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"></line>
                        <line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-toggle">
                    <button class="lang-btn active" data-lang="en">EN</button>
                    <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="ar">AR</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="marble-texture"></div>
        <div class="floating-shapes">
            <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
            <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
            <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="hero-subtitle" data-i18n="hero-subtitle">Premium Egyptian Natural Stone</p>
            <h1 class="hero-title" data-i18n="hero-title">Timeless <span>Elegance</span><br>Carved in Stone</h1>
            <p class="hero-description" data-i18n="hero-description">
                For over two decades, EMC has been transforming spaces with Egypt's finest marble and granite.
                We bring the timeless beauty of natural stone to luxury projects worldwide.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
                <a href="#products" class="btn btn-primary" data-i18n="hero-btn-explore">Explore Collection</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary" data-i18n="hero-btn-quote">Get a Quote</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">
            <span data-i18n="scroll">Scroll</span>
            <div class="scroll-line"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <span class="section-label" data-i18n="about-label">Our Story</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="about-title">A Legacy of Excellence</h2>
            <div class="section-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-content reveal">
                <h3 data-i18n="about-heading">Crafting Dreams in Stone Since 2000</h3>
                <p data-i18n="about-p1">
                    Founded in 2015, EMC builds upon the rich legacy of EMCO, our predecessor company
                    that has operated successfully since 2000. With over two decades of expertise in the
                    Egyptian marble and granite industry, we have established ourselves as a leading force
                    in natural stone excellence.
                </p>
                <p data-i18n="about-p2">
                    We specialize in the import and export of high-quality marble and granite, catering to
                    both domestic and international clients. Our commitment to excellence extends to marble
                    construction projects, where we deliver unparalleled craftsmanship and service.
                </p>
                <p data-i18n="about-p3">
                    Our vision is to be the premier provider of exquisite marble and granite solutions,
                    recognized globally for our commitment to quality, innovation, and sustainability.
                </p>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">25+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="stat-years">Years Experience</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">50+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="stat-varieties">Stone Varieties</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">30+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label" data-i18n="stat-countries">Countries Served</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-visual reveal">
                <div class="about-image about-image-1">
                    <span class="image-placeholder" data-i18n="img-quarry">Galala Marble Quarry</span>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image about-image-2">
                    <span class="image-placeholder" data-i18n="img-craft">Craftsmanship</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Products Section -->
    <section class="products" id="products">
        <div class="products-wrapper">
            <div class="section-header reveal">
                <span class="section-label" data-i18n="products-label">Our Collection</span>
                <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="products-title">Premium Egyptian Stone</h2>
                <div class="section-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-categories reveal">
                <button class="category-btn active" data-category="all" data-i18n="cat-all">All</button>
                <button class="category-btn" data-category="marble" data-i18n="cat-marble">Marble</button>
                <button class="category-btn" data-category="granite" data-i18n="cat-granite">Granite</button>
                <button class="category-btn" data-category="other" data-i18n="cat-other">Other Stones</button>
            </div>
            <div class="products-grid reveal">
                <!-- Marble Products -->
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-galala"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-galala">Galala Classic</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-sunny"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-sunny">Sunny Marble</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-sinai"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-sinai">Sinai Pearl</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-grey"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-milly">Milly Grey</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-imprador"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-imprador">Imprador</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="marble">
                    <div class="product-image img-breccia"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-breccia">Breccia</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-marble">Egyptian Marble</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Granite Products -->
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-black"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-blackstar">Black Star</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-halayb"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-halayb">New Halayb</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-rosa"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-rosa">Rosa Nasr</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-red"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-redroyal">Red Royal</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-verdi"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-verdi">Verdi Green</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="granite">
                    <div class="product-image img-gold-sinai"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-goldsinai">Golden Sinai</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-granite">Egyptian Granite</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Other Stones -->
                <div class="product-card" data-category="other">
                    <div class="product-image img-sandstone"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-hashma">Hashma Sandstone</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-sandstone">Natural Sandstone</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="other">
                    <div class="product-image img-basalt"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-basalt">Egyptian Basalt</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-igneous">Igneous Rock</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card" data-category="other">
                    <div class="product-image img-mica"></div>
                    <div class="product-info">
                        <h3 class="product-name" data-i18n="prod-mica">Mica Stone</h3>
                        <span class="product-type" data-i18n="type-sedimentary">Sedimentary Rock</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
            <span class="section-label" data-i18n="services-label">What We Offer</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="services-title">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="section-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="services-grid reveal">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                        <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                        <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 data-i18n="service-1-title">Import & Export</h3>
                <p data-i18n="service-1-desc">Global distribution of premium Egyptian marble and granite. We handle logistics and delivery to any destination worldwide.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                        <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
                        <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 data-i18n="service-2-title">Custom Fabrication</h3>
                <p data-i18n="service-2-desc">Precision cutting and finishing for any specification. Polished, honed, brushed, flamed, or sandblasted surfaces.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
                        <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 data-i18n="service-3-title">Project Consultation</h3>
                <p data-i18n="service-3-desc">Expert guidance for architects and designers. From material selection to installation support for luxury projects.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                        <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 data-i18n="service-4-title">Timely Delivery</h3>
                <p data-i18n="service-4-desc">Efficient supply chain management ensuring your materials arrive on schedule, every time.</p>
